OL,5, A grieving mother's campaign to help   
OL,6, lower the risk of accidental drowning  
OL,7, in lakes and reservoirs is to be       
OL,8, discussed by politicians.              
OL,10,FMark Allen, 18, died after jumping into
OL,11,Fa reservoir to cool off on a hot summer
OL,12,Fday in 2018 while out with friends.    
OL,14,FMum Leeanne Bartley is now fighting for
OL,15,Femergency throwlines to be installed   
OL,16,Fnext to every lake in the UK.          
OL,18,F"If there was rescue equipment, we     
OL,19,Fbelieve there would be a strong chance 
OL,20,Fhe'd still be with us today," she said.
